menu_sectionTitle.title: Show menu for {relativeTime}
menu_sectionTitle.note: Button text in a section heading to show a menu. The placeholder {relativeTime} will dynamically be replaced with values such as 'Today', 'Tomorrow', 'Yesterday', 'In 2 days', etc. For example, if {relativeTime} = 'Tomorrow', the title will become 'Show menu for Tomorrow'.

empty_title.title: Nothing to see here!
empty_title.note: Text shown where there are no remaining history items

delete_all.title: Delete All
delete_all.note: Text for a button that deletes all items or entries.

delete_some.title: Delete
delete_some.note: Text for a button that deletes currently selected items

delete_none.title: Nothing to delete
delete_none.note: Title/tooltip text on a button that does nothing when there is no browsing history to delete

show_history_all.title: Show all history
show_history_all.note: Button text for an action that removes all filters and searches, and replaces the list will all history.

show_history_older.title: Show older history
show_history_older.note: Button that shows older history entries

show_history_for.title: Show history for {range}
show_history_for.note: The placeholder {range} in the title will be dynamically replaced with specific date ranges such as 'Today', 'Yesterday', or days of the week like 'Monday'. For example, if the range is set to 'Today', the title will become 'Show history for Today'.

delete_history_all.title: Delete all history
delete_history_all.note: Button text for an action that removes all history entries.

delete_history_older.title: Delete older history
delete_history_older.note: Button that deletes older history entries.

delete_history_for.title: Delete history for {range}
delete_history_for.note: The placeholder {range} in the title will be dynamically replaced with specific date ranges such as 'Today', 'Yesterday', or days of the week like 'Monday'. For example, if the range is set to 'Today', the title will become 'Delete history for Today'.
